Package: scMethrix
Title: Fast and efficient summarization of single cell whole genome bisulfate data
Version: 0.1.0.0001
Authors@R: 
    person("Lindsay","Andrew", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "a.lindsay@dkfz.de", comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-6607-5812")) 
Description: This package summarizes single cell bisulfite data as stored in bedgraph files generated from multiple upstream pipelines. Available functions include: subsetting, filtering, imputing, clustering, and binning. Summarized data can be exported in multiple formats.
License: Apache License (>= 2)
Encoding: UTF-8
